title: RIP MY SHRED STICK: SANTA MONICA
description: Every Santa Monica grom that wasn't stuck in 405 Carmageddon or watching the new Harry Potter movie -- which ended up being about 20 kids -- was at the beach this morning for Hurley's second to last stop of the RMSS Tour. Click into the story for full highlights and photos from RMSS Santa Monica. Photos/video: PK.
